{"tid":1960080,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"點解旺角騷亂會叫魚蛋革命","createTime":"2020-04-06T01:56:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-12T05:25:37.000Z","uid":165028,"like":0,"dislike":46,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"fb4eebe50c5bbbc7a57c1f3d5b38a1fd78aa6dda","tid":1960080,"uid":165028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T01:56:11.000Z","msg":"我唔係要搵交嗌<br />\n只不過想搞清件事<br />\n一直都冇source講呢樣嘢<br />\n就算SCMP都只係叫 MongKok riot"},{"pid":"dc0965fbd360f2edfa04750384a8589078e27cdb","tid":1960080,"uid":138197,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T01:57:23.000Z","msg":"由一串魚蛋開始"},{"pid":"7aa666424aa31d007c25de416234e0f03b368f26","tid":1960080,"uid":48234,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T01:57:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">連<br />\n登<br />\n日<br />\n報<br />\n｜<br />\n支<br />\n持<br />\n獨<br />\n裁<br />\n政<br />\n權<br />\n者<br />\n，<br />\n無<br />\n權<br />\n享<br />\n有<br />\n言<br />\n論<br />\n自<br />\n由<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1180589\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1180589</a><br />\n請<br />\n問<br />\n天安門旅遊<br />\n(會員#165028)<br />\n你<br />\n屙<br />\n尿<br />\n嗰<br />\n陣<br />\n起<br />\n左<br />\n腳<br />\n定<br />\n右<br />\n腳<br />\n?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1767140\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1767140</a></span></span>"},{"pid":"007c32b531da9bd37e37f92a8994621f2fde963e","tid":1960080,"uid":195,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T01:58:35.000Z","msg":"會員 #165028 - 何東精神（團結）<br />\n，前稱純正港人(港豬)，離地中產，天安門旅遊，Frizzle(港豬)，Alexander(離地)極有可能係五毛, 分化撚, mon-post狗或網軍, 請大家多加注意!<br />\n該會員以往言論：<br />\n<br />\n<code>#1 - 周街都貼連豬搞到心都煩哂</code><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1677596/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1677596/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<blockquote>睇見隻豬就火滾想撕左佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<code>#1 - 誠哥真係好醒目</code><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1628499/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1628499/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<blockquote>開金口講句要對年青人網開一面<br />\n而家旗下百佳, 豐澤等避開一劫<br />\n如果唔係被暴徒燒毀打爛唔知幾多間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我而家見到黑衫蒙面阻住我架車都唔出聲屌佢地<br />\n作狀支持佢地俾個like 等佢地放行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<code>#1 - 想同琴晚太子站嘅一個勇武道歉</code><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1526091/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1526091/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<blockquote>因為我當時太驚又怕死<br />\n所以同其他乘客撞你出門口<br />\n希望你無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原諒我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<code>#1 - 好怕d勇武派</code><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1503651/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1503651/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<blockquote>街上面見到佢地都會避之則吉<br />\n怕會招惹埋d警察<br />\n琴日黃大仙站成班又面罩又防具咁衝入車廂<br />\n嚇到我下個站即刻落車</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<code>#1 - （求屌醒）一直唔明白你地搞抗爭做咩</code><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1320673/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1320673/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<blockquote>我80後 本身都係中產階級 收入穩定又係專業人士<br />\n雖然近呢個月都聽左好多理據話要爭取好多野<br />\n包括撤回逃犯條例 調整警權過大 之類<br />\n但係我就唔明點解一定要搞到武力衝突先收手<br />\n再加上止舉令警民官民矛盾越來越大 對香港真係好咩<br />\n<br />\n點解要搞咁多野 真心唔明每個星期搞一兩單衝突暴動真係好咩 已經港九新界都搞砸哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">#1 - 想報仇</code></pre><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1767121\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1767121</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>發現女朋友個WhatsApp 有同第二個男仔有纏綿對話<br />\n我知道個男仔有參加社會又搞衝擊<br />\n宜家想搞佢罪証再報警篤灰</blockquote>"},{"pid":"e6dfc2fe04e5781b64a36043b9ab0974e81a8d11","tid":1960080,"uid":74622,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T02:02:26.000Z","msg":"其實唔使下下上連登問<br />\n自己Google下 已經有<br />\n<a href=\"https://evchk.wikia.org/zh/wiki/%E9%AD%9A%E8%9B%8B%E9%9D%A9%E5%91%BD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fevchk.wikia.org%2Fzh%2Fwiki%2F%25E9%25AD%259A%25E8%259B%258B%25E9%259D%25A9%25E5%2591%25BD&d=IFfiXVp8wSeEFxWCfbiPLUXxRC0ARC%2FjKSdqd%2FiyNcw%3D&h=e08c58cf\" target=\"_blank\">https://evchk.wikia.org/zh/wiki/%E9%AD%9A%E8%9B%8B%E9%9D%A9%E5%91%BD</a>"},{"pid":"3b04a224197e1290006fa9eb8288d7464c27e5a5","tid":1960080,"uid":165028,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"e6dfc2fe04e5781b64a36043b9ab0974e81a8d11","tid":1960080,"uid":74622,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T02:02:26.000Z","msg":"其實唔使下下上連登問<br />\n自己Google下 已經有<br />\n<a href=\"https://evchk.wikia.org/zh/wiki/%E9%AD%9A%E8%9B%8B%E9%9D%A9%E5%91%BD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fevchk.wikia.org%2Fzh%2Fwiki%2F%25E9%25AD%259A%25E8%259B%258B%25E9%259D%25A9%25E5%2591%25BD&d=IFfiXVp8wSeEFxWCfbiPLUXxRC0ARC%2FjKSdqd%2FiyNcw%3D&h=e08c58cf\" target=\"_blank\">https://evchk.wikia.org/zh/wiki/%E9%AD%9A%E8%9B%8B%E9%9D%A9%E5%91%BD</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T02:06:34.000Z","msg":"其實點解要反抗<br />\n食環捉小販好似冇咩問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7f45f52e4be28bf1f49afc6c468889ceed3b099","tid":1960080,"uid":144522,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T02:07:23.000Z","msg":"屌你scmp <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c9c7fbfee976b1067fd8f47cb7e35a1bb910ce2","tid":1960080,"uid":74622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b04a224197e1290006fa9eb8288d7464c27e5a5","tid":1960080,"uid":165028,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"e6dfc2fe04e5781b64a36043b9ab0974e81a8d11","tid":1960080,"uid":74622,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTi